Use the generating function
\[
\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}\binom{2n}{n}x^n=\frac{1}{\sqrt{1-4x}},\qquad |x|<\frac14.
\]
Here \(x=\frac15\), which satisfies \(\left|\frac15\right|<\frac14\). Thus
\[
\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}\binom{2n}{n}\frac{1}{5^n}
=\frac{1}{\sqrt{1-4\cdot \frac15}}
=\frac{1}{\sqrt{1-\frac45}}
=\frac{1}{\sqrt{\frac15}}
=\sqrt{5}.
\]

